  Ti7 hit-e5 kiong5-koan5 tok8-chhai5 e5 si5-tai7, ti7 hit e5 hun3-khai3 pi-siong e5 koaN5-thiN, Bok8-su khi3 tham3-hong2 Lim5 Gi7-hiong5 sian-siN liau2-au7, che7 ti7 Tai5-pak Chhia-thau5 tui3-bin7 e5 Hi-luh-thng teh lim ka-pi. Hit-si5 chin chiap-kin7 Khu-li-suh-ma-suh, sim-cheng5 khiok si7 chin tim5-tang7. Ka-pi-thiaN u7 1-ui7 sio2-chia2 teh chau3 “5 11 32 11, 5 6 1 6 5” chit-siu2 Seng3-tan7 koa. Tong-si5 u7 chin-che7 goa7-kok-lang5, sou2-i2 sio2-chia2 eng7 chiok-che7 kok gi2-gian5 teh chhiuN3. Bo5-i3-kou3, hiong5-hiong5 thiaN-tioh8 toaN5 kng3-khim5 e5 sio2-chia2 teh chhiuN3, “Ti7 chit8-e5 be2-cho5--nih8, bo5 io5-na5 thang eng7.......”. Bok8-su kong2 i hoaN-hi2 kah siuN7 beh chau2-khi3 kah hit-e5 sio2-chia2 chim--1--e7.
